{"tid":2334264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"挑戰緊急法蒙面法失敗 終院裁定政府勝訴","createTime":"2020-12-21T05:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T06:26:50.000Z","uid":272531,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2ff120843a517bc49afb39e33027c9a3d90c00cf","tid":2334264,"uid":272531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:15:47.000Z","msg":"政府去年針對反修例抗爭，動用近半世紀未曾用過的緊急法訂立蒙面法，聲稱為要試圖遏止暴力示威，泛民就此提請司法覆核。案件上訴至終審法院，終院今頒判詞，五名法官一致裁定政府勝訴，緊急法合憲，而蒙面法禁止在合法和非法遊行集會蒙面，亦屬合憲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/FRQFQU2DO5BTDI4YUNL7A6YVKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FFRQFQU2DO5BTDI4YUNL7A6YVKA%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzAHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=8771e263\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FFRQFQU2DO5BTDI4YUNL7A6YVKA%2F&h=ef9021b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/FRQFQU2DO5BTDI4YUNL7A6YVKA/</a><br />\n<br />\n合法與非法遊行集會皆不可蒙面"},{"pid":"4eac326e15b6ca743c35afc3fc63c0a5e565ada3","tid":2334264,"uid":272531,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:15:54.000Z","msg":"德國1933年授權法：容許納粹德國總理阿道夫&middot;希特拉及其內閣無須經由議會審議而通過任何法案，只需其領導的內閣通過及公佈即成為法律，而國會並沒有推翻的權力。"},{"pid":"6e084d87ba0b0edf2d660b9f4ce588f80d26763c","tid":2334264,"uid":316927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:21:49.000Z","msg":"行政做埋立法機關都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cae5fbb08527bd62c906b3bdd88c766bf8d2225","tid":2334264,"uid":108247,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"連登仔：馬道立已經俾政府收買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33f2c32f8d2eb0f0f42b060f6d7ff033a527866","tid":2334264,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eac326e15b6ca743c35afc3fc63c0a5e565ada3","tid":2334264,"uid":272531,"like